DUE TO THE SIGNIFICANT IMPACT OF THE ECONOMIC

DOWNTURN IN THE FOURTH-QUARTER OF 2008 ON SALES AND OPERATING INCOME RESULTS,

THE FOLLOWING DISCUSSES BOTH FOURTH-QUARTER 2008 AND TOTAL YEAR 2008 RESULTS

FOR EACH BUSINESS SEGMENT.

INDUSTRIAL

AND TRANSPORTATION BUSINESS (30.9% OF CONSOLIDATED SALES).

