MANUFACTURES AND MARKETS PERSONAL PROTECTION AND ENERGY ABSORBING PRODUCTS 

FOR APPROXIMATELY $1.2 BILLION, INCLUSIVE OF DEBT ASSUMED, WHICH WAS

IMMEDIATELY PAID OFF.

