·

PHARMACEUTICALS BUSINESS ACTIONS  EMPLOYEE-RELATED,

ASSET IMPAIRMENT AND OTHER COSTS PERTAINING TO THE COMPANYS EXIT OF ITS

BRANDED PHARMACEUTICALS OPERATIONS. THESE COSTS INCLUDED SEVERANCE AND BENEFITS

FOR PHARMACEUTICALS BUSINESS EMPLOYEES WHO ARE NOT OBTAINING EMPLOYMENT WITH

THE BUYERS AS WELL AS IMPAIRMENT CHARGES ASSOCIATED WITH CERTAIN ASSETS NOT

TRANSFERRED TO THE BUYERS.

